Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
data.Vehicle
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bus, Taxi, Train
public abstract class Vehicle extends Object
Abstract class that represents a generic vehicle. Contains basic attributes such as ID, ability, cost, model, and brand.
